        "text": [
          "ه عن حمدان بن الحسين فقد رويته عن عليّ بن حاتم إجازة قال: أخبرنا القاسم بن محمّد قال: حدّثنا حمدان بن الحسين‌."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "And whatever is narrated from Hamdan ibn Al-Husayn, I have narrated it from Ali ibn Hatim by authorization, who said: Al-Qasim ibn Muhammad informed us, who said: Hamdan ibn Al-Husayn narrated to us."
